---
name: 05-gen-data-test
version: 1.1.0
preamble-tier: 2
description: >
  Tao bo du lieu kiem thu tu danh sach test case.
  Ho tro 2 che do output:
  - minimal: chi 1 file master dataset
  - full: master dataset + coverage map + data-driven + teardown + manifest
---

## Quy tac luu output
- Neu can ghi output ra file/thu muc, phai tu tao day du thu muc dich neu chua ton tai.

## Quy tac ngon ngu
- Noi dung output viet bang tieng Viet co dau.
- Giu nguyen khong dau cho ma ky thuat: ID, endpoint, field name, status code, keyword he thong, ten file.

## Dau vao
- Danh sach test case (bat buoc)
- Mo ta truong du lieu (type/constraint/format) (khuyen nghi)
- Thong tin moi truong DB/API (khuyen nghi)
- Yeu cau data sensitivity/PII (khuyen nghi)

## Output mode (bat buoc)
- Skill ho tro 2 che do:
  - `minimal`: chi tao 1 file duy nhat la master dataset TSV
  - `full`: tao day du artifact traceability
- Thu tu uu tien xac dinh mode:
  1. user chi dinh truc tiep (`minimal`/`full`)
  2. `qa-config.yaml` co khoa `test_data.output_mode`
  3. mac dinh = `minimal`
- Neu user noi ro "chi can 1 file" thi bat buoc dung `minimal`.

## Nguyen tac sinh data
- Cu the, khong dung placeholder chung chung.
- PII-safe, khong dung data that production.
- Co BVA/EP khi test case yeu cau.
- Data co the reset, khong phu thuoc thu tu chay.

## Format output theo mode

### Mode `minimal` (mac dinh)
Tao duy nhat 1 file:
```tsv
TC_ID\tDataset_ID\tTen truong\tGia tri\tLoai\tGhi chu
```
Loai: `BVA-min` / `BVA-max` / `BVA-min-1` / `BVA-max+1` / `EP-valid` / `EP-invalid` / `Corner` / `Normal`

### Mode `full`
- Phan 1: Master dataset TSV
- Phan 2: TC Coverage Map
- Phan 3: Data-Driven table
- Phan 4: Teardown script
- Them manifest yaml ket qua run

## Luu file vao
Dung `output_paths.test_data` tu qa-config (mac dinh: `testing-output/test-data/`).

- mode `minimal`:
  - `master-dataset-{project.sprint}-v{semver}-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}.tsv`

- mode `full`:
  - `master-dataset-{project.sprint}-v{semver}-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}.tsv`
  - `tc-coverage-map-{project.sprint}-v{semver}-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}.tsv`
  - `data-driven-table-{project.sprint}-v{semver}-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}.tsv`
  - `teardown-{project.sprint}-v{semver}-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}.sql`
  - `data-generation-result-{yyyy-mm-dd}_{HHmm}-R{N}.yaml`

## Completion Status
- `DONE`
  - mode `minimal`: tao xong 1 file master dataset hop le, parse duoc theo TC.
  - mode `full`: day du bo file theo quy dinh, khong thieu artifact bat buoc.
- `DONE_WITH_CONCERNS`: co canh bao (thieu constraint, teardown chua map DB that, v.v.).
- `BLOCKED`: thieu input toi thieu.
- `NEEDS_CONTEXT`: can bo sung mo ta field/constraint/environment.

## Checklist xac nhan luu file dung chuan
- [ ] Da luu vao dung thu muc `testing-output/test-data/` hoac path override
- [ ] Dung ten file theo mode da chon
- [ ] mode `minimal`: chi con 1 file master dataset
- [ ] mode `full`: du master + coverage + data-driven + teardown + manifest
- [ ] Da kiem tra lai version, timestamp, sprint trong ten file
